Category:       Language

Executable CEquiv
   main-is: src/CEquiv.hs
   build-depends: base, filepath, mtl, pretty, language-c, language-c-test
   if impl(ghc >= 8.0)
     ghc-options:    -rtsopts -Wall -Wno-redundant-constraints
   else
     ghc-options:    -rtsopts -Wall

